{
  "final_answer": "Here are AMD's revenue guidance ranges and their sizes as a percentage of the midpoint for each period:\n\n**Q2 2024:** $5.4 billion (low) to $6.0 billion (high), 10.53% of midpoint\n**Q3 2024:** $6.4 billion (low) to $7.0 billion (high), 8.96% of midpoint\n**Q4 2024:** $7.2 billion (low) to $7.8 billion (high), 8.00% of midpoint\n**Q1 2025:** $6.8 billion (low) to $7.4 billion (high), 8.45% of midpoint\n\n**Calculations:**\n\n| Period | Low | High | Midpoint | Range (High - Low) | Range as % of Midpoint |\n|--------|-----|------|----------|-------------------|----------------------|\n| Q2 2024 | $5.4B | $6.0B | $5.7B | $0.6B | 0.6/5.7 = 10.53% |\n| Q3 2024 | $6.4B | $7.0B | $6.7B | $0.6B | 0.6/6.7 = 8.96% |\n| Q4 2024 | $7.2B | $7.8B | $7.5B | $0.6B | 0.6/7.5 = 8.00% |\n| Q1 2025 | $6.8B | $7.4B | $7.1B | $0.6B | 0.6/7.1 = 8.45% |\n\n**Sources:**\n\n- **Q2 2024 guidance** was provided during AMD's Q1 2024 earnings release on April 30, 2024. The guidance was stated as \"approximately $5.7 billion, plus or minus $300 million\" (range $5.4B to $6.0B). Source confirms: Seeking Alpha / multiple financial press (Yahoo Finance, Benzinga, Sahm Capital).\n- **Q3 2024 guidance** was provided during AMD's Q2 2024 earnings press release on July 30, 2024. Stated as \"approximately $6.7 billion, plus or minus $300 million\" (range $6.4B to $7.0B). Source: AMD Q2 2024 press release on GlobeNewswire.\n- **Q4 2024 guidance** was provided during AMD's Q3 2024 earnings press release on October 29, 2024. Stated as \"approximately $7.5 billion, plus or minus $300 million\" (range $7.2B to $7.8B). Source: AMD Q3 2024 press release on GlobeNewswire.\n- **Q1 2025 guidance** was provided during AMD's Q4 2024 earnings release on February 4, 2025. Stated as \"approximately $7.1 billion, plus or minus $300 million\" (range $6.8B to $7.4B). Source: CNBC, The Motley Fool, Communications Today.\n\n{\n    \"sources\": [\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/07/30/2921412/0/en/amd-reports-second-quarter-2024-financial-results.html\",\n            \"name\": \"AMD Reports Second Quarter 2024 Financial Results (contains Q3 2024 guidance)\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2024/10/29/2971245/0/en/AMD-Reports-Third-Quarter-2024-Financial-Results.html\",\n            \"name\": \"AMD Reports Third Quarter 2024 Financial Results (contains Q4 2024 guidance)\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://www.cnbc.com/2025/02/04/amd-earnings-report-q4-2024.html\",\n            \"name\": \"AMD earnings report Q4 2024 (contains Q1 2025 guidance)\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/amd-beats-on-q1-revenue-and-eps-stock-edges-lower-on-light-guidance-202840712.html\",\n            \"name\": \"Yahoo Finance - AMD Q1 2024 earnings (contains Q2 2024 guidance)\"\n        },\n        {\n            \"url\": \"https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/analyst-color/24/07/40018437/amd-q2-earnings-preview-microsoft-impact-data-center-guidance-on-watch-analyst-warn\",\n            \"name\": \"Benzinga - AMD Q2 Earnings Preview (confirms Q2 2024 guidance range)\"\n        }\n    ]\n}",
